{
  "stem": "20035.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And from there on they closed the door.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "As they close the door, that they put in a pail of water, one pail of water.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't have to tell you that after going and marching, and everybody carrying-- that once again, the order was the one suitcase, you were allowed to carry.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was able to carry, with my brother, mom's suitcase.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I can't remember who it was carrying mom's and who was carrying grandpa's.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because both of us were strong, I carried my own.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And naturally, we could carry mom-- dad carried his own.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we get on the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And suddenly, that pail of water I have never seen one person drinking, everybody dipped their hand in it and wiped their mouth and probably their tongue, a little bit, a drop or two of water.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that pail of water went around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Everybody had a chance to do it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But then that pail of water, by the evening-- this was early in the morning when we went, or before noon-- by the evening became the only possibility of having-- going to the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the-- the-- I mean, the humility suddenly, when you see people whom you-- not only that you know, but you respect, that it should be your mother's age, your father, your grandparents' age.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Those people were sheltered by a coat or by something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And suddenly, they had to go and-- and do what-- well, the minimum at least, we knew.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we grew up, and every human being in the normal condition knows that the minimum personal place where you can be.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
